Requirements:

- a standard installation of OCaml
- an implementation of a DBM library such as GDBM
- ocaml-dbm [godi] - may be already included in the main OCaml package
- ocamlfind [godi]
- omake [godi]
- lwt [godi]
- cohttp [https://github.com/avsm/ocaml-cohttp]
- cohttpserver [https://github.com/avsm/ocaml-cohttpserver]
- yojson and dependencies [godi]


Compilation:

  $ omake

Installation:

  $ omake install
or
  $ omake BINDIR=/foo/bin install

Uninstallation:

  $ omake uninstall
